title: IBM WDA280 content dump
description:
This torrent contains files from hard disk drive that i found in trash container with remains of crushed old notebook.
The hard drive is 2,5" IDE (PIO mode 4) IBM WDA-280 for notebook and has above 80 megabytes of size. I connect this drive to my HP Vectra VL400 through adapter and dump all content. Disk is still work, have no problems.
The text files and Word documents in Russian
